<plot>A child is playing with his crayons and doodling whatever comes to mind. Out of sight, his parents begin to have a noisy argument the child can't avoid. The emotional tension from that exchange spills over into his art as he is affected by it so much that the art begins a nightmare overwhelming his sense of reality.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?290930</url></doc>
